messages.message: :jenkins::broom: we are going to conduct a jenkins house cleaning to delete the deprecated jenkins jobs and groovy scripts from our repo in the next two weeks, please take a look at the worksheet (https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1eelnPcJic3r-gNC3WjRT6tJMBOri_xIzp-bnAJB3338/edit#gid=1035495262) and find the job that you are working with, make a comment if we need to keep it, otherwise jobs that haven't executed for more than 2 months will be deleted along with its groovy file in instabase repo, please feel free to reach out to <#C035SLYCJ9X|> for questions
